            <title>[FLINK-1549] Add proper exception handling for YarnJobManager</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1549</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The YarnJobManager actor thread calls methods which can throw an exception. These exceptions should be caught and properly handled.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
